ActHealth of Animals Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the HEALTH OF ANIMALS REGULATIONS to the extent that all veterinary laboratories in Canada will be required to notify the Canadian Food Inspection Agency when certain animal diseases are diagnosed or suspected, and by establishing two lists of animal diseases, the Immediately Notifiable Diseases List and the Annually Notifiable Diseases List.
